% 宏包中所有选项均为小写。
%^^A! In \CTeX{} bundle, the correspoding options are \opt{UTF8} and
%^^A! \opt{GBK}. Note that all the options in \pkg{zhlipsum} are in
%^^A! \emph{lowercase}.
%^^A!
